Global Safety Management Program «5 Stars» gives the 14th power plant in Riyadh an excellent rating

07 Nov 2019, 00:06

The 14th power plant project in Riyadh, which is affiliated with the Saudi Electricity Company, has received an excellent evaluation in the audit of the Global Safety Management Program “5 Stars”. Saudi EPCM's national cadres, whose percentage of Saudization in the plant exceeded 85 per cent. This is in addition to the series of achievements of the station team, which succeeded during the last period in the operation of the first units of the station;
